These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, juice
1. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | juice | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, designer
1. the security-guard is on the left or right of the designer##3
2. the designer is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | security-guard | designer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | traveling | hiking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, dubstep
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | hip-hop |

 #################################

 
